articles.title: Car owner sues Tesla over alleged intrusion of privacy - Al Jazeera English
articles.description: Lawsuit filed after reports alleged Tesla employees privately shared videos and images recorded by vehicle cameras.
articles.content:
A California-based owner of a Tesla vehicle has sued the electric carmaker in a prospective class action lawsuit accusing it of violating the privacy of customers.
